lting in a physical interpretation in terms of regions of\nthe spectrum that affected its decision, making it no longer a black box. These\nregions coincide with those used by human experts such as relevant spectral\nlines, and are even used in a similar way, with the classifier e.g. effectively\nmeasuring the width of a line by weighing its center and its tails oppositely.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Apr 2021 18:25:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-04"}
