tential can reproduce many\ncloud properties, but additional physical processes are needed to fully explain\nthe gas structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Apr 2021 18:42:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Dec 2022 11:43:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-21"}
