umes up to 3x larger, models with 25% more depth, or models with up to 2x\nthe number of channels than a corresponding non-reversible network.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Apr 2021 21:23:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Apr 2021 01:02:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-22"}
