n of the same elements from the remaining host glass. Based on our\nresults, we develop a mechanistic model that explains the high tendency of RE3+\nto form clusters in alkali aluminoborosilicate glasses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Apr 2021 21:32:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-21"}
